this page</a> should you wish to do so.</i></dd></dl>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Fires a shard of alchemical ice that coats whatever it hits with a layer of brittle frost which slows their movement.\n<p>Each shot fired will deplete the cannon's remaining durability, but if it survives to fire 5 times, the final shot will fragment to hit all enemies around the primary target for additional damage.\n</p>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Hoarfrost Bullet</b> is a monster-only spell which deals <a href=\"/Cold\" title=\"Cold\">cold</a> damage, automatically hits, and inflicts the <a href=\"/Frozen\" title=\"Frozen\">Frozen</a> status.\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Hoarfrost Bullet:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">I</span> <a href=\"/File:Hoarfrost_cannon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hoarfrost cannon.png\" src=\"/images/0/0b/Hoarfrost_cannon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Hoarfrost_cannon\" title=\"Hoarfrost cannon\">Hoarfrost cannon</a></b> (3d9 damage)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">0.32</a>, this spell will be added to the game as part of <a href=\"/Hoarfrost_Cannonade\" title=\"Hoarfrost Cannonade\">Hoarfrost Cannonade</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916113132\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.212 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 303/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2504/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 461/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.080s\nLua virtual si